The paper proposes a decoding algorithm for neural generation and evaluates it on tasks such as dialogue response generation, abstractive summarization, and machine translation. These tasks are typically associated with the arXiv CS sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
